Package: img2mp4
Architecture: all
Depends: 
    bash,
    bash-shlib,
    python3-pil,
    ffmpeg,
    ${python3:Depends}, 
    ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: bash-completion, exiftool
Description: Convert image series to video with timecode as subtitle
 img2mp4 converts a series of images into a video file with timecode
 subtitles extracted from EXIF data or file modification times.
 .
 Features:
  - Extract timestamps from EXIF data or file modification time
  - Multiple subtitle themes (split, simple, large)
  - Support for H.264 and H.265 codecs
  - Configurable frame rate, resolution, and quality
  - Automatic timezone detection

